Theme Selection

Callout Logic

Modern LIMS: Keeps the color coding but desaturates it massively.
  • Purple: Become a faint lavender wash.
  • Red: Becomes a soft Rose.
  • Borders: Very subtle, just to define the area.
  • This preserves the "Quick Scan" ability without the "Neon Glare".
Draft Mode ID: EXP-2023-884

CRISPR-Cas9 Gene Knockout Protocol

Demonstrating admonition/callout styles in context.
description Abstract
This protocol details the transfection of HEK293 cells using a high-fidelity Cas9 RNP complex. The primary objective is to achieve a knockout efficiency >80% while maintaining cell viability above 90%.

Prepare the workspace by cleaning all surfaces with 70% ethanol. Retrieve the Cas9 protein and sgRNA aliquots from the -80C freezer.

edit_note Calculation Example
To achieve a 1:1.2 molar ratio:
Volume of Cas9 (61 kDa): 2.5 L
Volume of sgRNA (32 kDa): 1.8 L
check_circle Quality Check Passed
RNP complex formation confirmed via gel electrophoresis showing a clear shift in band migration compared to apo-Cas9.
warning Biohazard Warning
Lentiviral vectors can integrate into human DNA. Handle all materials in a Biosafety Level 2 (BSL-2) laminar flow hood. Dispose of waste in biohazard containers immediately.
bug_report Known Issue
Batch #4492 of the Electroporation Buffer has shown reduced conductivity. Verify pH is 7.4 before use.
